# Candidates

<aside class="notice">
  Required scope: Admin
</aside>

A candidate is defined by a unqiue email adress. If a candidate don't have any <code>job-applications</code> it can be either <code>sourced</code> or <code>connected</code>.

* When <code>sourced</code> the candidate was added to the system by a recruiter.<br>
* When <code>referred</code> the candidate was added to the system by an employee.
* When <code>connected</code> the candidate has opted in to recieve new job notifications and has also the option to create a richer and more personal profile.

